  "description": "One of the older models in the Serie 4 refrigerator family from Bosch, introduced to the market in 2019. At the same time, the device boasts both good camera capacity and fairly advanced functionality. So, the total useful volume of the Bosch KGN39XL316 refrigerator is 366 liters. The manufacturer provides two separate cooling circuits for each of the working chambers, so that you can completely independently control the operating modes of the refrigeration and freezer compartments. The freezing compartment itself with a volume of 87 liters is located below, and its capacity is quite enough to completely freeze up to 14 kg of fresh food per day. As for the refrigerator compartment, its capacity is 255 liters, and inside there is a special freshness zone (zero chamber for 24 liters), designed for the longest possible storage of fresh vegetables and fruits. The Multi Air Flow dynamic cooling system ensures even distribution of cold air throughout the entire volume. The control panel is external, touch-sensitive, the level of noise generated during operation does not exceed 39 dB, energy consumption corresponds to class A ++.",
